1
00:00:06,520 --> 00:00:08,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我從一開始就公開說過</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

2
00:00:08,520 --> 00:00:10,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我是腦癌患者</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

3
00:00:10,320 --> 00:00:12,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>想要尋找自然療法治癒自己</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

4
00:00:12,600 --> 00:00:14,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我問過腫瘤醫生飲食的事，她翻白眼</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

5
00:00:15,040 --> 00:00:17,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他們對營養的知識怎麼能這麼淺薄？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

6
00:00:17,680 --> 00:00:19,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>真是有夠傲慢</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

7
00:00:19,520 --> 00:00:22,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>蜜拉手臂上的腫塊是侵襲性腫瘤</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

8
00:00:22,120 --> 00:00:25,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>大範圍切除</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>更能避免腫瘤擴散到手臂之外</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

9
00:00:25,120 --> 00:00:27,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>人生中最悽慘的情況之一</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

10
00:00:27,760 --> 00:00:30,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>就發生在我身上，我對此充滿感激</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

11
00:00:30,360 --> 00:00:32,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我不認為這是正確的做法</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

12
00:00:32,520 --> 00:00:35,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-我要其他選擇</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-死亡那是另一個選擇</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

13
00:00:35,280 --> 00:00:37,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你得了惡性腦癌</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

14
00:00:37,320 --> 00:00:39,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>只剩下六星期的壽命，最多四個月</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

15
00:00:39,480 --> 00:00:41,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>告訴你想要我怎麼做</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

16
00:00:41,520 --> 00:00:43,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-我會照辦</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-我要她身敗名裂</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

17
00:00:43,440 --> 00:00:44,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你聽過貝兒吉柏森嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

18
00:00:44,720 --> 00:00:47,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-你覺得她怎麼樣？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-也許是榨財的吸血蟲</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

19
00:00:47,120 --> 00:00:48,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>甚至是居心不良的毒蛇</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

20
00:00:48,360 --> 00:00:51,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我絞盡腦汁討他們的歡心</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

21
00:00:51,440 --> 00:00:54,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>可到頭來，他們從來沒喜歡過我</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

22
00:00:56,440 --> 00:00:58,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（以下劇情來自真實故事的啟發）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

23
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:03,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（某些角色與事件為創作與虛構）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

24
00:01:08,920 --> 00:01:10,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我必須找到正確的方法</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

25
00:01:11,920 --> 00:01:12,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>為了我自己</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

26
00:01:13,800 --> 00:01:15,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那個地方叫做赫希研究所</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

27
00:01:15,880 --> 00:01:17,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是位於墨西哥的治療計畫</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

28
00:01:18,400 --> 00:01:19,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>超級嚴格</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

29
00:01:19,760 --> 00:01:21,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>需要大量勞動</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

30
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:22,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>必須經過篩選</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

31
00:01:23,640 --> 00:01:25,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他們並非來者不拒</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

32
00:01:27,600 --> 00:01:30,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我父親華特，是德國人</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

33
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:31,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>有猶太血統</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

34
00:01:31,800 --> 00:01:34,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他在第一次世界大戰後三餐不繼</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

35
00:01:34,600 --> 00:01:39,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>然而，就在他挨餓的階段</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>他的身體開始痊癒</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

36
00:01:39,720 --> 00:01:42,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>在因緣際會下</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

37
00:01:42,160 --> 00:01:44,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>華特來到美國</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

38
00:01:44,520 --> 00:01:47,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他們告訴我父親</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>“華特，你不能行醫</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

39
00:01:47,760 --> 00:01:50,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你不會說英文”，所以他開始學英語</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

40
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:53,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他們又說：“華特，你不能行醫</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

41
00:01:53,880 --> 00:01:56,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你不是註冊的美國醫生”</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

42
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:59,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>然後他以優異成績</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>通過美國醫師資格考</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

43
00:01:59,880 --> 00:02:03,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>最後，他終於可以開業了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

44
00:02:03,240 --> 00:02:07,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他只透過飲食的方式治癒癌症患者</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

45
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:09,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>就這麼簡單</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

46
00:02:09,920 --> 00:02:15,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>問題來了</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>美國醫學會對他的知識感興趣嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

47
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:18,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>答案是否定的，他們關閉了他的診所</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

48
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:22,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>因為他們認為</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

49
00:02:22,480 --> 00:02:26,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>只有他們的藥才能治好癌症</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

50
00:02:26,640 --> 00:02:27,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你們知道嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

51
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:33,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>百分之90的腫瘤科醫生</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>會在有選擇的情況下拒絕化療</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

52
00:02:34,040 --> 00:02:36,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是真的，你可以上網自己查</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

53
00:02:37,080 --> 00:02:41,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我父親不相信那種醫學</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

54
00:02:41,880 --> 00:02:44,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>因為他知道真相</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

55
00:02:44,880 --> 00:02:47,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>人類擁有自癒能力</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

56
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:50,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>只要我們能跟自然界達成和諧狀態</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

57
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:54,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>所有答案都存在大自然中</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

58
00:02:54,920 --> 00:02:57,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>只要你加以留心</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

59
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:08,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這是根據謊言改編的真實故事</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

60
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:12,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>切記真相很少純粹，也絕不簡單</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

61
00:03:12,880 --> 00:03:15,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-有些名字經過修改，人物為虛構…</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-露西</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

62
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:18,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>呼吸急促的狀況怎麼樣？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

63
00:03:18,320 --> 00:03:19,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>應該差不多吧</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

64
00:03:20,760 --> 00:03:23,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我在想可能有點傷到動脈</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

65
00:03:23,600 --> 00:03:26,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>有時候做放療會這樣</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我已經幫你安排做心電圖了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

66
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:28,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

67
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:29,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>謝謝</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

68
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:33,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她有承認說謊嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

69
00:03:33,280 --> 00:03:34,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她會寧願吃碎玻璃</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

70
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:37,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>天啊，我身上好臭</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

71
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:39,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我的鐵蛋白偏低</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>所以我最近吃了更多肉</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

72
00:03:39,600 --> 00:03:41,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-還好啦</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-死亡動物的氣息從我的毛孔竄出</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

73
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:43,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>所以你覺得她撒謊？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

74
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:45,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不是覺得，我知道這是事實</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

75
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:47,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>怎麼會？你們是好朋友嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

76
00:03:47,320 --> 00:03:48,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們有相同的刺青</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

77
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:51,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>最近有沒有吵架？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

78
00:03:51,880 --> 00:03:55,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>抱歉，你覺得我會為了小小的爭吵</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>大費周章跑來嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

79
00:03:57,160 --> 00:03:59,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你們必須了解一點</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

80
00:04:01,760 --> 00:04:03,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒沒有朋友</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

81
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:05,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>只有宿主</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

82
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:10,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們要接她的案子嗎？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>這個澳洲肖婆？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

83
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:12,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>當然不要</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

84
00:04:13,480 --> 00:04:17,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>而且只有當她認為你有利用價值時</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

85
00:04:18,080 --> 00:04:20,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她才會千方百計黏上去</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

86
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:30,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>嘿</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

87
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:32,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你還好嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

88
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:35,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我叫的車一直取消</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

89
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:38,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我可能焦慮症發作了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

90
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:41,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我以前從來沒這樣過</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

91
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:43,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>深呼吸</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

92
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:47,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>當她試圖遮掩時，就是經過精心算計</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

93
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:49,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-你要去哪裡？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-不用了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

94
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:52,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我不想麻煩你</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

95
00:04:52,840 --> 00:04:55,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>也許你會對她產生同情</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

96
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:57,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>或是想跟她打一砲</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

97
00:04:58,000 --> 00:05:00,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這是一大失策，我聽人家這樣說</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

98
00:05:01,920 --> 00:05:03,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她在床上像條死魚，懂吧？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

99
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:05,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>沒有批判的意思</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

100
00:05:05,080 --> 00:05:07,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>又或者你會受寵若驚</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

101
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:10,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>因為她表現出很感興趣的樣子</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

102
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:13,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你有兒子還是女兒？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

103
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:16,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我有…女兒</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

104
00:05:17,320 --> 00:05:18,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對，兩個</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

105
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:21,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我就知道，你有爸爸的氣質</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

106
00:05:22,640 --> 00:05:23,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>想進來喝一杯嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

107
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:28,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不了，我不能進去</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

108
00:05:28,080 --> 00:05:31,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>就她好像能看到你身上</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>別人看不到的東西</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

109
00:05:32,160 --> 00:05:33,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>弱點</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

110
00:05:33,520 --> 00:05:34,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你今天可以不用見我的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

111
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:37,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你人真的很好</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

112
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:39,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那是一種把戲</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

113
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:41,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這是你家嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

114
00:05:41,880 --> 00:05:43,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>因為不知不覺中</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

115
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:45,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你已經開始竭盡全力</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>滿足她的所有需求</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

116
00:05:45,840 --> 00:05:47,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>而且相信我，需求多不勝數</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

117
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:50,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>有個領域是你可以接受訪談</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

118
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:52,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>在你能操控的環境裡</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

119
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:55,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>自己挑選記者，先看過問題</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

120
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:57,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們可以這樣嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

121
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:58,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那也太棒了吧</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

122
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:02,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是你，不是我們</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

123
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:04,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>可能吧</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

124
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:07,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>最終她能找到37種不同的方式</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

125
00:06:07,080 --> 00:06:08,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>同時扮演英雄與受害者</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

126
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:12,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>美國的情況很不一樣</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>你可以擁有目標</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

127
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:15,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>在國內</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我們會毀掉任何得意忘形的人</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

128
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:17,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>再加上一點厭女心態？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

129
00:06:17,960 --> 00:06:20,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>有哪個年輕女性</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>敢在商業界有所作為？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

130
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:23,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他們完全誤解了我的理念</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

131
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:25,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我不在乎錢</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

132
00:06:25,320 --> 00:06:28,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>同樣地，我從來就不想談論癌症</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

133
00:06:28,400 --> 00:06:31,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我只是想分享好起來的秘訣</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

134
00:06:31,760 --> 00:06:33,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>給人們得到健康的工具</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

135
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:37,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我可沒叫他們喝漂白水</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>或把咖啡灌進肛門</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

136
00:06:37,640 --> 00:06:39,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>如果你喜歡說一聲</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我請人送一箱過去</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

137
00:06:39,840 --> 00:06:42,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我沒有叫任何人停藥</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

138
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:44,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>手機應用程式和書</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

139
00:06:44,880 --> 00:06:46,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>都是健康食譜而已，海克</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

140
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:52,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這種事不容易證實</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

141
00:06:54,400 --> 00:06:55,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我可以公開具名</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

142
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:56,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>即便如此也一樣</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

143
00:06:56,880 --> 00:06:59,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>從道德和法律層面來說</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

144
00:06:59,080 --> 00:07:01,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們不能公開指控某人的健康狀況</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

145
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:03,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>除非有事實可佐證</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

146
00:07:03,640 --> 00:07:06,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>如果她昨天才被診斷出罹癌呢？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

147
00:07:06,080 --> 00:07:08,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-認真嗎？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-或是她精神不正常呢？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

148
00:07:08,080 --> 00:07:10,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她還是在說謊，而且持續很多年了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

149
00:07:10,880 --> 00:07:13,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們的律師會說我們需要病歷</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

150
00:07:13,320 --> 00:07:16,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-你知道她的腫瘤科醫生的名字嗎？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-她沒有醫生</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

151
00:07:16,080 --> 00:07:17,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這就是我的重點</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

152
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:21,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>聽著，這是大新聞</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

153
00:07:22,040 --> 00:07:23,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

154
00:07:23,400 --> 00:07:26,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那些放任她這麼做的粉絲和組織…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

155
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:30,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>為什麼他們不更關心</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>去檢驗她的說法是否屬實？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

156
00:07:30,880 --> 00:07:32,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我又為什麼沒去查？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

157
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:34,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我又不笨，也不是特別好騙</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

158
00:07:34,760 --> 00:07:36,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但顯然我是傻瓜</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

159
00:07:36,760 --> 00:07:37,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>真他媽的蠢</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

160
00:07:39,160 --> 00:07:42,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我喜歡這個故事</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>漂亮的照片，她用的字體很有品味</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

161
00:07:42,520 --> 00:07:45,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我把她推薦給健康不佳的人</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

162
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:47,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>為此我永遠無法原諒我自己</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

163
00:07:49,160 --> 00:07:50,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你明白嗎？她…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

164
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:54,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她的謊言可能正在害死人</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

165
00:07:54,880 --> 00:07:56,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她在害死人</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

166
00:08:02,080 --> 00:08:03,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們來測試一下</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

167
00:08:06,280 --> 00:08:07,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（搜尋：貝兒吉柏森）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

168
00:08:09,840 --> 00:08:16,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好，我查到健康廚坊</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>在2012年1月16日註冊成商業名稱</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

169
00:08:16,240 --> 00:08:19,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不，貝兒早在那之前就行騙了</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>在IG最初興起的時候</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

170
00:08:19,880 --> 00:08:24,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>2010年還有另一家公司註冊</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>有信用問題，名稱是</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

171
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:26,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>有機寶貝</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

172
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:27,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那是什麼？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

173
00:08:28,640 --> 00:08:29,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>2010年</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

174
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:32,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好，貝兒，當時你是誰？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

175
00:08:32,680 --> 00:08:34,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（貝兒吉柏森臉書）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

176
00:08:38,800 --> 00:08:42,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>深入探索最尖端的</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>社交媒體最佳化策略</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

177
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:44,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>以促進業務成長和影響力</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

178
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:46,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>歡迎各位創新者</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

179
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:49,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>此刻人們正在談論你的品牌</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

180
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:52,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>也在談論你</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

181
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:54,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但臉書要怎麼幫你拉更多生意？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

182
00:08:55,560 --> 00:08:58,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你想在推特上說什麼？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>推特到底什麼東東？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

183
00:08:58,680 --> 00:09:00,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>它能撐下去嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

184
00:09:00,080 --> 00:09:02,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>網站，銷售的基礎…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

185
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:06,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>克萊夫，我想系統需要重新啟動</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

186
00:09:07,360 --> 00:09:09,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>抱歉，各位，技術性問題</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

187
00:09:09,640 --> 00:09:12,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>為資訊科技忍者克萊夫鼓鼓掌</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

188
00:09:12,920 --> 00:09:15,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他是我們數位代理公司的支柱</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

189
00:09:16,040 --> 00:09:18,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>在我們等待的時候，歡迎提問</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

190
00:09:18,440 --> 00:09:20,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>該不該做連結場？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

191
00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:33,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>給你，否則你沒空吃</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

192
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:36,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我想請教一下</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>你們主攻入口網站，對吧？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

193
00:09:36,800 --> 00:09:40,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我很好奇要怎麼避免它們</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>不受谷歌改變演算法的影響？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

194
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:43,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這個啊，避免不了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

195
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:45,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-真的嗎？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-對</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

196
00:09:45,400 --> 00:09:47,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你的商業模式真是有趣</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

197
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:50,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我只是他們的員工，但的確很有趣</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

198
00:09:50,560 --> 00:09:51,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我是貝兒</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

199
00:09:52,880 --> 00:09:56,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我一直在開發個人網路商店</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

200
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:59,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-是嗎？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-名稱是有機寶貝</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

201
00:09:59,160 --> 00:10:01,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我花了很多心力做網站最佳化</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

202
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:03,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但後端程式方面我一竅不通</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

203
00:10:04,040 --> 00:10:04,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>購物車</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

204
00:10:04,960 --> 00:10:07,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不，那東西還挺…不好搞，對吧？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

205
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:09,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-對，我的頭都快爆炸了</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-我懂</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

206
00:10:10,520 --> 00:10:12,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你見過路克嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

207
00:10:12,120 --> 00:10:15,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-你應該去找他</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-我比較想跟你談</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

208
00:10:16,680 --> 00:10:18,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你是支柱，對吧？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

209
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:24,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是啊</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

210
00:10:24,520 --> 00:10:25,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你有名片嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

211
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:01,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（嘿，蜜拉）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

212
00:11:01,400 --> 00:11:04,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（會議很爛）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

213
00:11:04,800 --> 00:11:08,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（沒有人懂任何東西）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

214
00:11:08,520 --> 00:11:11,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（輪到我們表現了）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

215
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:14,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（親親 貝兒）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

216
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:32,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>嗨，小寶貝</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

217
00:11:33,520 --> 00:11:34,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>爸爸呢？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

218
00:11:34,840 --> 00:11:37,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>希望他沒有讓你看一整天電視</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

219
00:11:44,400 --> 00:11:45,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>嗨</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

220
00:11:45,400 --> 00:11:46,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>怎樣？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

221
00:11:48,680 --> 00:11:52,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-你沒發現他需要換尿布嗎？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-尿布沒了，我正要去買</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

222
00:11:52,280 --> 00:11:54,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-奈森，你不能讓他泡在屎裡</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-貝兒，今天夠累了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

223
00:11:55,640 --> 00:11:56,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

224
00:11:57,320 --> 00:11:58,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你今天做了什麼？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

225
00:11:58,600 --> 00:12:00,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們出去散步，我換了床單</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

226
00:12:00,760 --> 00:12:02,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不用換床單</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

227
00:12:02,360 --> 00:12:04,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>當然要換床單，怎樣？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

228
00:12:04,600 --> 00:12:06,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這是基本的衛生習慣</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>每兩到三週要換一次</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

229
00:12:07,040 --> 00:12:08,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>一定要換床單</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

230
00:12:09,560 --> 00:12:11,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>半小時後回來</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

231
00:12:14,320 --> 00:12:16,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我好像養了兩個小孩</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

232
00:12:16,920 --> 00:12:20,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我的要求不高</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>只要多幫一點忙就行了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

233
00:12:20,160 --> 00:12:21,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>哪怕只多一點都好</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

234
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:25,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不管如何</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我已經開始想開車撞倒班了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

235
00:12:26,600 --> 00:12:27,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不是每天這麼想</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

236
00:12:27,520 --> 00:12:30,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>只在他能一個人開車去上班的日子</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

237
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:33,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-還有開午餐會議時</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-天啊，是的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

238
00:12:34,120 --> 00:12:37,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>同時，我跟他媽媽和我媽</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>一起困在家裡</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

239
00:12:37,480 --> 00:12:39,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>真不知道為什麼要搬回布萊頓</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

240
00:12:39,560 --> 00:12:41,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我沒想過會這麼辛苦</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

241
00:12:41,800 --> 00:12:44,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>在家帶小孩，而不是去工作</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

242
00:12:44,840 --> 00:12:47,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>知道嗎，我必須帶小孩還要兼顧工作</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

243
00:12:47,600 --> 00:12:49,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>至少你不是餵母乳</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>你們晚上可以輪流餵奶</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

244
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:52,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>糟糕，灑出來了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

245
00:12:54,600 --> 00:12:56,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這就是我的生活寫照，抱歉</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

246
00:12:58,120 --> 00:12:59,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>有人需要嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

247
00:12:59,480 --> 00:13:01,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我要開始在我的網站上販售</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>叫有機寶貝</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

248
00:13:02,680 --> 00:13:04,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>已經是谷歌關鍵字排名第一名</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

249
00:13:04,680 --> 00:13:06,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-第一名？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-對</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

250
00:13:06,760 --> 00:13:07,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>太厲害了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

251
00:13:07,880 --> 00:13:10,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我只需要找個倉庫</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>就可以開始進口了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

252
00:13:10,720 --> 00:13:14,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>寶寶的衣服</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>還有產前和產後服用的維他命</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

253
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:15,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>純天然牙膠玩具</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

254
00:13:16,040 --> 00:13:18,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-你怎麼這麼忙？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-我有健康問題</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

255
00:13:19,240 --> 00:13:22,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我得替我兒子創造收入來源</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>以防萬一</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

256
00:13:29,120 --> 00:13:30,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>抱歉，我沒有餵母乳</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

257
00:13:30,520 --> 00:13:31,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我真是個差勁的母親</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

258
00:13:31,960 --> 00:13:34,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我的寶寶沒有吸吮反射</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

259
00:13:34,360 --> 00:13:37,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-我相信她不是在…</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-批判嗎？但她明明就是</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

260
00:13:37,920 --> 00:13:41,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>抱歉我沒用該死的名牌嬰兒推車</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>在布萊頓也沒有該死的房子</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

261
00:13:41,760 --> 00:13:43,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我必須工作</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

262
00:13:43,240 --> 00:13:44,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我也想工作</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

263
00:13:44,800 --> 00:13:47,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>娜塔莎不是那種人</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>你看得出來她忙到分身乏術</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

264
00:13:47,880 --> 00:13:50,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>如果你們不合拍</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

265
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:52,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>可能只是年齡差異吧</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

266
00:13:53,720 --> 00:13:56,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>為什麼？我23歲了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

267
00:13:57,480 --> 00:13:58,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我以為你才19歲</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

268
00:14:00,120 --> 00:14:03,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我23歲，很多女人23歲就生小孩</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

269
00:14:03,160 --> 00:14:05,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對，這我知道，我只是說</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

270
00:14:05,400 --> 00:14:07,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>也許你可以找另一個團體</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

271
00:14:07,800 --> 00:14:10,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>加入兩個團體沒什麼不好</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

272
00:14:10,680 --> 00:14:13,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-抱歉，我只是…</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-對，不用了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

273
00:14:14,600 --> 00:14:16,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我睡眠嚴重不足</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

274
00:14:16,320 --> 00:14:17,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你兒子的頭是扁的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

275
00:14:19,040 --> 00:14:20,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你得幫他翻身</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

276
00:14:43,920 --> 00:14:45,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你是世界上最棒的寶寶</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

277
00:14:47,080 --> 00:14:49,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你不需要其他寶寶</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

278
00:14:50,640 --> 00:14:52,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你是最乖的寶寶</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

279
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:55,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>乖到不行的小寶貝</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

280
00:14:59,800 --> 00:15:02,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你女兒還小時</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>你太太在家帶小孩嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

281
00:15:04,520 --> 00:15:06,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>沒有，我們輪流</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

282
00:15:07,520 --> 00:15:08,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-很好</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-對</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

283
00:15:10,960 --> 00:15:12,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我當時應該做更多的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

284
00:15:14,160 --> 00:15:15,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她在心理治療時這麼說</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

285
00:15:21,480 --> 00:15:24,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我產後三星期就回去工作了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

286
00:15:25,360 --> 00:15:26,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>其他人有…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

287
00:15:27,440 --> 00:15:29,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>家人或社群</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

288
00:15:29,680 --> 00:15:31,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>之類的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

289
00:15:33,760 --> 00:15:36,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我受困在一段糟糕的感情裡</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

290
00:15:36,840 --> 00:15:37,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>人生一蹋糊塗</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

291
00:15:40,760 --> 00:15:41,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我就是這樣長大的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

292
00:15:43,720 --> 00:15:45,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我不希望我的孩子過這種日子</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

293
00:15:49,600 --> 00:15:52,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>如果我跟蜜拉住在同一個城市</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>情況應該會大不相同</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

294
00:15:53,480 --> 00:15:55,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們在網上認識，但後來變得很親密</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

295
00:15:58,280 --> 00:15:59,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她自己也有健康問題</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

296
00:16:00,520 --> 00:16:04,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但更重要的是，我們互相支持</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

297
00:16:05,440 --> 00:16:08,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>而且我總是為蜜拉的成就歡欣鼓舞</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

298
00:16:08,760 --> 00:16:11,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（你進入赫希了？）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

299
00:16:11,160 --> 00:16:13,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（我的天，也太棒了！）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

300
00:16:13,960 --> 00:16:17,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（謝謝，親愛的</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>愛你 很多個吻）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

301
00:16:28,680 --> 00:16:30,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我的確需要你幫忙盤點</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

302
00:16:30,680 --> 00:16:31,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>伊莎貝兒？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

303
00:16:31,600 --> 00:16:33,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我有告訴你蜜拉進入赫希了嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

304
00:16:34,080 --> 00:16:35,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那是一項全人照護的治療計畫</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

305
00:16:35,800 --> 00:16:37,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>在提吉華納，他們不是來者不拒</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

306
00:16:37,840 --> 00:16:40,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>念成提華納，發音像大麻</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

307
00:16:42,840 --> 00:16:46,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>明年可能會去</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>等我們打過旅遊疫苗後</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

308
00:16:46,280 --> 00:16:48,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不用跑去那麼遠的健康水療中心</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

309
00:16:49,680 --> 00:16:50,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那是癌症診所</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

310
00:16:52,040 --> 00:16:54,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>為什麼我去不呢，瑪格麗特？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

311
00:16:57,280 --> 00:16:59,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好了，吃午餐去</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

312
00:16:59,840 --> 00:17:01,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>還沒到11點</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

313
00:17:01,480 --> 00:17:03,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我五點要做治療</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

314
00:17:03,080 --> 00:17:05,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>食物消化需要時間</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>所以我現在要吃午餐</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

315
00:17:06,920 --> 00:17:08,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我有存貨不見了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

316
00:17:09,000 --> 00:17:11,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>什麼？不，我有跟你說</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

317
00:17:12,720 --> 00:17:14,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我借了幾條嬰兒包巾</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

318
00:17:14,120 --> 00:17:17,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>還有六件法國名牌小號童裝</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我沒說是你偷的，伊莎貝兒</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

319
00:17:17,920 --> 00:17:19,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>因為我帶回家拍照</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

320
00:17:19,760 --> 00:17:21,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>要給你們商店網站用的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

321
00:17:21,920 --> 00:17:23,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這裡，自己看</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

322
00:17:23,200 --> 00:17:24,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我沒要你這麼做</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

323
00:17:24,560 --> 00:17:26,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你故步自封，而且自己都沒意識到</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

324
00:17:27,040 --> 00:17:29,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>實體零售店頂多再撐三到五年</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

325
00:17:30,080 --> 00:17:31,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你需要我，瑪格麗特</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

326
00:17:33,360 --> 00:17:34,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-你到底有沒有偷？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-沒有</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

327
00:17:34,720 --> 00:17:36,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那她就是胡說八道</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

328
00:17:36,240 --> 00:17:40,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-非法解僱，我們把她告上法院</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-我們哪來的錢？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

329
00:17:40,240 --> 00:17:42,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-我去找工作</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-你以前都找不到了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

330
00:17:42,360 --> 00:17:45,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-是你自己想要去上班的</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-我有一個四個月大的孩子</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

331
00:17:45,440 --> 00:17:46,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我也是</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

332
00:17:46,360 --> 00:17:48,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你以為我想賺13.51元的時薪嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

333
00:17:48,480 --> 00:17:50,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我想建立有意義、能長久延續的東西</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

334
00:17:51,560 --> 00:17:53,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我不是說他打過我</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

335
00:17:57,640 --> 00:17:59,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒，你能不能…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

336
00:18:00,200 --> 00:18:01,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒，開門</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

337
00:18:01,520 --> 00:18:03,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他媽的開門！</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

338
00:18:04,920 --> 00:18:07,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好了，沒事</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

339
00:18:11,320 --> 00:18:13,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>媽，我不知道該怎麼辦</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

340
00:18:13,320 --> 00:18:14,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她瘋了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

341
00:18:17,640 --> 00:18:19,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（蜜拉？需要你，寶貝）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

342
00:18:19,760 --> 00:18:22,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（我不知道該怎麼辦）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

343
00:18:23,040 --> 00:18:25,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>乖啦，沒事了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

344
00:18:26,600 --> 00:18:27,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>蜜拉有回訊息</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

345
00:18:28,840 --> 00:18:29,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>當然啦</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

346
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:33,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是15天後，說句公道話，她很忙</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

347
00:18:36,520 --> 00:18:38,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>所以是8000元</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

348
00:18:38,640 --> 00:18:40,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>8000美元</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

349
00:18:40,760 --> 00:18:43,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-多久？兩星期嗎？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-三星期</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

350
00:18:43,280 --> 00:18:45,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>三星期？加上去墨西哥的機票</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

351
00:18:45,800 --> 00:18:47,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們應該能用哩程數換</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

352
00:18:47,400 --> 00:18:49,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-我已經存五千塊了</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-我也能出一點</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

353
00:18:50,040 --> 00:18:52,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>等到部落格的粉絲數達到兩萬</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>就能吸引廣告商</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

354
00:18:52,960 --> 00:18:55,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不行，你可以去度個假</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

355
00:18:56,400 --> 00:18:58,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但我們必須找正統的醫生</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

356
00:18:58,280 --> 00:18:59,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>因為你很懂嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

357
00:19:00,400 --> 00:19:02,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我傳的研究報告你都沒看</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

358
00:19:02,360 --> 00:19:04,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那是果汁，就這樣嗎？喝果汁？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

359
00:19:04,480 --> 00:19:08,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是嗎？我現在就去商店買</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>你想喝多少我都可以幫你榨</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

360
00:19:08,640 --> 00:19:11,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但你必須回去找修醫生</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

361
00:19:11,200 --> 00:19:15,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>聽著，蓋房子時</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>要僱用有建築執照的人</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

362
00:19:15,640 --> 00:19:16,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-爸</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-什麼？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

363
00:19:16,760 --> 00:19:18,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這不是房子</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

364
00:19:18,280 --> 00:19:19,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-聽著</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-這是我的身體</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

365
00:19:19,840 --> 00:19:23,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>當你要牽管線時</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>需要找水管工、技師</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

366
00:19:23,160 --> 00:19:24,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>懂門道的人</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

367
00:19:24,560 --> 00:19:27,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>如果有人答應你好到不真實的事</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

368
00:19:27,560 --> 00:19:29,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你知道怎樣嗎，蜜拉？就不是真的！</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

369
00:19:32,520 --> 00:19:33,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>可惡</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

370
00:19:37,560 --> 00:19:41,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（蜜拉布萊克</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>健康的敵人是負能量）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

371
00:19:46,480 --> 00:19:49,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他認為醫生是神</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>他不夠聰明，不會質疑他們</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

372
00:19:49,320 --> 00:19:50,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好了，小聲一點</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

373
00:19:51,480 --> 00:19:53,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>聽著，他只是一時情緒失控</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

374
00:19:54,960 --> 00:19:57,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他愛你勝過世上任何事物</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

375
00:19:57,960 --> 00:20:01,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>聽著，我知道你們為我犧牲多少</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

376
00:20:01,760 --> 00:20:05,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我看過你們把我的教育擺在第一位</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

377
00:20:05,200 --> 00:20:08,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但你們這麼做不就是希望</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我有獨立做決定的能力嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

378
00:20:08,840 --> 00:20:12,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我可以查資料</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>研讀科學理論，了解內容</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

379
00:20:12,200 --> 00:20:14,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-我不想死，因為…</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-我們不聊這個</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

380
00:20:14,560 --> 00:20:15,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>媽，我必須說出來</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

381
00:20:18,040 --> 00:20:20,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我不想死或放棄等死</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

382
00:20:20,560 --> 00:20:22,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>只因為他不懂科學原理</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

383
00:20:26,760 --> 00:20:29,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我不會讓她逼迫我們接受</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

384
00:20:30,760 --> 00:20:31,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我明天打給修醫生</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

385
00:20:31,960 --> 00:20:34,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他能提供關於這家赫希機構的意見</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

386
00:20:34,840 --> 00:20:36,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他會知道所有細節</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

387
00:20:46,240 --> 00:20:48,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你在做什麼，瘋子？現在是大半夜！</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

388
00:20:50,240 --> 00:20:51,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>媽</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

389
00:20:55,600 --> 00:20:56,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>媽</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

390
00:21:00,280 --> 00:21:02,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我要動用你外婆的錢</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

391
00:21:04,600 --> 00:21:05,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她會很高興的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

392
00:21:07,080 --> 00:21:07,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>真的嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

393
00:21:10,160 --> 00:21:12,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我這輩子還沒去過墨西哥</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

394
00:21:15,680 --> 00:21:16,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>謝謝</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

395
00:21:17,760 --> 00:21:18,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不客氣</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

396
00:21:20,320 --> 00:21:22,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>新鮮的蔬果</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

397
00:21:23,360 --> 00:21:25,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>沒有噴灑殺蟲劑</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

398
00:21:25,240 --> 00:21:27,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>只要正確食用</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

399
00:21:27,160 --> 00:21:29,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>就能修復身體的DNA損傷</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

400
00:21:30,520 --> 00:21:32,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>在赫希研究所</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

401
00:21:32,160 --> 00:21:35,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們提供支持與工具</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

402
00:21:35,280 --> 00:21:39,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>療癒你的身體，從內而外徹底改變</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

403
00:21:39,520 --> 00:21:41,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你的生活方式</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

404
00:21:42,840 --> 00:21:43,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（墨西哥歡迎你）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

405
00:21:43,800 --> 00:21:44,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（提華納歡迎你）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

406
00:21:45,000 --> 00:21:47,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（不敢相信我在這裡！）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

407
00:21:47,240 --> 00:21:49,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（真替你開心！）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

408
00:22:08,400 --> 00:22:10,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我以為它會更像醫院</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

409
00:22:19,360 --> 00:22:21,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（融入赫希）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

410
00:22:21,680 --> 00:22:23,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（BELLEG1991：好嫉妒！）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

411
00:22:24,200 --> 00:22:27,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>各種咖啡都適合</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>從金黃、綠色、白色</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

412
00:22:27,480 --> 00:22:29,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>到淺烘焙和中烘焙</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

413
00:22:29,520 --> 00:22:30,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但深度烘焙不適合</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

414
00:22:31,040 --> 00:22:33,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>因為強效化合物</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>已經因為烘烤破壞了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

415
00:22:33,400 --> 00:22:34,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>咖啡應該是有機的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

416
00:22:34,800 --> 00:22:36,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們推薦使用公平交易</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>注重永續性的咖啡豆</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

417
00:22:37,000 --> 00:22:39,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>所以沒有雀巢咖啡或摩可納咖啡嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

418
00:22:39,080 --> 00:22:41,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我要外帶一杯濃的脫脂拿鐵灌進肛門</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

419
00:22:43,000 --> 00:22:44,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>也許用點潤滑劑吧</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

420
00:22:51,040 --> 00:22:52,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>會痛嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

421
00:22:53,520 --> 00:22:54,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不會，沒事</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

422
00:22:57,240 --> 00:23:01,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>等我老了、不中用了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

423
00:23:01,720 --> 00:23:03,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>換你為我做這種事</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

424
00:23:05,720 --> 00:23:06,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我會在這裡的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

425
00:23:07,840 --> 00:23:08,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我知道你會</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

426
00:23:14,560 --> 00:23:16,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>該倒滿杯了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

427
00:23:16,320 --> 00:23:17,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-好</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-沒錯</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

428
00:23:17,760 --> 00:23:19,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-那是…</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-來吧</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

429
00:23:19,720 --> 00:23:22,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不行，這樣不乖</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>那太…我想守規矩</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

430
00:23:22,200 --> 00:23:24,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-想要更多嗎？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-小心倒</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

431
00:23:25,320 --> 00:23:26,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-沒關係</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-你的杯子呢？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

432
00:23:29,360 --> 00:23:32,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你可以喝我的，好嗎？只要…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

433
00:23:33,440 --> 00:23:34,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你回來了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

434
00:23:36,040 --> 00:23:37,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不是要去動物園嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

435
00:23:37,960 --> 00:23:39,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他肚子有點痛</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

436
00:23:40,400 --> 00:23:41,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你好，我是海克曼</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

437
00:23:41,880 --> 00:23:44,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>天啊，我好像認識你很久了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

438
00:23:44,280 --> 00:23:46,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這位是那家厲害公關公司的海克</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

439
00:23:46,400 --> 00:23:49,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們將要合作，應該吧，希望如此</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

440
00:23:49,520 --> 00:23:51,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-我最好去把他放下來</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-好</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

441
00:23:51,560 --> 00:23:52,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>要不要讓我來？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

442
00:23:52,920 --> 00:23:54,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不用了，你去忙吧</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

443
00:23:58,200 --> 00:23:59,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-媽咪在工作嗎？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-對</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

444
00:24:00,320 --> 00:24:02,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我迫不及待想讓你們好好認識一下</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

445
00:24:03,680 --> 00:24:05,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你不是說你是單親媽媽？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

446
00:24:05,640 --> 00:24:07,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>奈森回墨爾本了，那是克萊夫</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

447
00:24:07,840 --> 00:24:08,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>原來是克萊夫</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

448
00:24:10,520 --> 00:24:11,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>克萊夫住在這裡？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

449
00:24:13,600 --> 00:24:14,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>當然</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

450
00:24:15,440 --> 00:24:16,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他是我的救命恩人</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

451
00:24:18,000 --> 00:24:18,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好吧</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

452
00:24:19,920 --> 00:24:21,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>快給我開門！</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

453
00:24:43,840 --> 00:24:46,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（克萊夫羅斯威爾）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

454
00:25:10,920 --> 00:25:12,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>謝謝</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

455
00:25:12,760 --> 00:25:14,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我是不是不請自來？天啊，貝兒</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

456
00:25:15,520 --> 00:25:18,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-清醒一點</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-反正我剛剛沒事</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

457
00:25:22,880 --> 00:25:24,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你有姊妹嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

458
00:25:24,800 --> 00:25:26,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我總是看得出來</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

459
00:25:27,160 --> 00:25:29,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我只有一個姊姊</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

460
00:25:29,760 --> 00:25:32,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>在阿得雷德跟我姊…跟我外甥女</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

461
00:25:34,120 --> 00:25:37,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>一個姊姊</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>兩個外甥女，住在阿得雷德</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

462
00:25:39,720 --> 00:25:40,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我就知道</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

463
00:25:44,000 --> 00:25:45,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>所以你…有什麼事…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

464
00:25:46,000 --> 00:25:48,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-你想讓我看你受到…</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-抱歉</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

465
00:25:54,160 --> 00:25:56,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這實在太難堪了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

466
00:26:03,720 --> 00:26:05,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>奈森不是壞人</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

467
00:26:06,360 --> 00:26:07,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>當我…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

468
00:26:07,800 --> 00:26:09,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>當我覺得不安全</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

469
00:26:10,080 --> 00:26:12,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>腎上腺素超過負荷時</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

470
00:26:13,080 --> 00:26:15,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我就無法冷靜思考</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

471
00:26:17,200 --> 00:26:18,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我有一些健康問題</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

472
00:26:19,280 --> 00:26:21,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你不必…不用說</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

473
00:26:21,880 --> 00:26:22,960
