482
00:27:26,160 --> 00:27:28,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我知道這只是嬰兒服裝</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

483
00:27:28,920 --> 00:27:30,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對世界沒多大貢獻</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

484
00:27:31,120 --> 00:27:31,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>做得很棒</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

485
00:27:33,920 --> 00:27:34,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>真的嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

