00:27:34,840 --> 00:27:36,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>簡潔、優雅</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

487
00:27:37,720 --> 00:27:39,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這都是你自己架設的？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

488
00:27:42,720 --> 00:27:43,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>怎麼會？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

489
00:27:47,920 --> 00:27:49,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>自學者嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

490
00:27:53,160 --> 00:27:54,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>自修來的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

491
00:28:23,720 --> 00:28:25,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>化療藥從這裡滴進去</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

492
00:28:26,200 --> 00:28:30,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>如果你不想，我們不必勉強做任何事</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

493
00:28:31,000 --> 00:28:32,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-我想要</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-是嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

494
00:28:32,600 --> 00:28:33,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>超想</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

495
00:28:40,920 --> 00:28:42,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>等等，我能不能…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

496
00:28:42,280 --> 00:28:44,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>能不能請問你幾歲？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

497
00:28:44,680 --> 00:28:47,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>因為我覺得我對你來說可能太老了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

498
00:28:51,000 --> 00:28:52,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我是個老靈魂</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

499
00:28:54,520 --> 00:28:56,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>而且我覺得你可能很完美</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

500
00:28:59,640 --> 00:29:00,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我快40歲了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

501
00:29:02,560 --> 00:29:03,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>真的嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

502
00:29:04,560 --> 00:29:06,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我會為你辦最好玩的派對</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

503
00:29:33,680 --> 00:29:36,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>想像如果這變成三人行</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

504
00:29:51,920 --> 00:29:53,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我醉了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

505
00:29:54,280 --> 00:29:56,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我要醒醒酒</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

506
00:30:00,120 --> 00:30:00,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>或者…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

507
00:30:03,440 --> 00:30:04,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我可以打電話給朋友</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

508
00:30:05,400 --> 00:30:06,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>有趣的朋友嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

509
00:30:08,480 --> 00:30:10,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對，他可以送貨到府</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

510
00:30:17,160 --> 00:30:18,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我就知道你是麻煩人物</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

511
00:30:21,080 --> 00:30:23,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我先給你一管，好嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

512
00:30:23,520 --> 00:30:25,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>因為你已經很亢奮了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

513
00:30:25,880 --> 00:30:27,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這不會傷害你的腦子嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

514
00:30:28,960 --> 00:30:30,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>如果你是我</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

515
00:30:31,160 --> 00:30:33,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你會意識到人生只有一次</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

516
00:30:35,760 --> 00:30:36,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不會吧！</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

517
00:30:50,480 --> 00:30:52,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>看看我的傷疤，你看！</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

518
00:30:53,000 --> 00:30:53,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>看得到嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

519
00:30:54,000 --> 00:30:56,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-我看不到！</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-因為你老了！這裡！</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

520
00:30:57,920 --> 00:31:00,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-那不是腫瘤！</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-是腫瘤！</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

521
00:31:00,240 --> 00:31:02,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-不是腫瘤！</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-是腫瘤！</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

522
00:31:12,840 --> 00:31:15,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>行了，應該都弄好了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

523
00:31:17,600 --> 00:31:18,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他幾點回來？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

524
00:31:19,840 --> 00:31:22,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-你聽說過IG嗎？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-什麼？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

525
00:31:23,400 --> 00:31:27,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>類似攝影應用程式Hipstamatic</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>但濾鏡更好</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

526
00:31:33,960 --> 00:31:36,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（用戶名稱：@BELLEINMELBOURNE）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

527
00:31:42,080 --> 00:31:43,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（3個讚）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

528
00:32:14,960 --> 00:32:16,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（療癒貝兒）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

529
00:32:16,440 --> 00:32:18,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（11個讚）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

530
00:32:21,200 --> 00:32:22,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>嗨，寶貝</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

