00:32:27,080 --> 00:32:28,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（#有機寶貝）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

532
00:32:28,720 --> 00:32:30,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（44個讚）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

533
00:32:44,360 --> 00:32:45,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（綠石療癒）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

534
00:32:45,680 --> 00:32:46,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（#擺脫癌症）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

535
00:32:46,920 --> 00:32:48,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（#赫希療法）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

536
00:32:48,440 --> 00:32:49,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（#拒絕化療）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

537
00:32:49,920 --> 00:32:52,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（#擺脫癌症1年）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

538
00:32:59,920 --> 00:33:01,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>謝謝</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

539
00:33:01,160 --> 00:33:02,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>六點來接你</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

540
00:33:02,480 --> 00:33:04,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>今天我要拆人工血管</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

541
00:33:04,800 --> 00:33:06,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>會耗很久，我們回家見</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

542
00:33:06,960 --> 00:33:09,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-你確定？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-愛你，給你一個大親親，再見</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

543
00:33:09,840 --> 00:33:11,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-再見</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-再見，寶貝</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

544
00:33:13,200 --> 00:33:17,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（癌症閃邊去）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

545
00:33:17,880 --> 00:33:21,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>蜜拉布萊克22歲時</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>被診斷出患有危及性命的肉瘤</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

546
00:33:22,000 --> 00:33:23,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她剛從墨西哥回來</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

547
00:33:23,360 --> 00:33:26,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>靠著純果汁飲食戰勝了癌症</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

548
00:33:26,240 --> 00:33:28,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她的網路人氣暴漲</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

549
00:33:28,800 --> 00:33:30,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>現在她有一本新書上架了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

550
00:33:31,000 --> 00:33:33,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-《從地獄到痊癒》，書名取得很好</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-謝謝</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

551
00:33:33,680 --> 00:33:35,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我看到停不下來</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

552
00:33:35,160 --> 00:33:37,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>能不能跟我們解釋一下</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>什麼是赫希療法？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

553
00:33:37,760 --> 00:33:40,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好的，這種療法讓癌細胞無法攝取</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

554
00:33:40,320 --> 00:33:41,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>成長所需的任何養分</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

555
00:33:42,040 --> 00:33:44,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>再用任何致它們於死的東西</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>加以滋養</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

556
00:33:44,720 --> 00:33:46,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>差不多是這樣，簡單來說</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

557
00:33:46,880 --> 00:33:48,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但背後有許多科學原理</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

558
00:33:48,560 --> 00:33:51,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-這是很重大的終生承諾</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-那當然</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

559
00:33:51,080 --> 00:33:54,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>整整兩年</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我們每天必須喝下13杯新鮮有機果汁</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

560
00:33:54,640 --> 00:33:56,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-天啊</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-每小時整點開喝</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

561
00:33:56,320 --> 00:33:59,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>外加每天進行五次的咖啡灌腸</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

562
00:33:59,880 --> 00:34:01,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-對</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-五次，我沒看錯吧？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

563
00:34:01,880 --> 00:34:04,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>還沒嘗試前，別先下定論</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>你想試試看嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

564
00:34:04,640 --> 00:34:06,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不了，我會整整失眠一星期</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

565
00:34:07,000 --> 00:34:09,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你的氣色真的很棒</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

566
00:34:09,960 --> 00:34:10,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>謝謝</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

567
00:34:11,960 --> 00:34:13,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>老實說，我的狀態不曾這麼好過</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

568
00:34:14,480 --> 00:34:17,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不只是因為擺脫癌症</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

569
00:34:18,360 --> 00:34:20,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我真的很慶幸我聆聽身體的聲音</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

570
00:34:20,440 --> 00:34:21,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>給了它需要的東西</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

571
00:34:23,520 --> 00:34:25,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你也很帥氣，我喜歡你的鬍子</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

572
00:34:25,600 --> 00:34:28,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>謝謝，這是我的文青風階段</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

573
00:34:28,800 --> 00:34:30,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我打算改走綠林好漢風</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

574
00:34:30,920 --> 00:34:32,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你想趁我們在這裡時去找她嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

575
00:34:33,120 --> 00:34:34,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她在布里斯本，對吧？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

576
00:34:34,640 --> 00:34:37,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對，我只是受邀參加媽媽的婚禮</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

577
00:34:37,280 --> 00:34:39,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>一定會是一場該死的鬧劇</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

578
00:34:39,600 --> 00:34:42,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒，別這樣，不要這麼消極</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

579
00:34:42,280 --> 00:34:44,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你根本不知道自己會碰上什麼</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

580
00:34:44,440 --> 00:34:46,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我很期待</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

581
00:34:46,880 --> 00:34:49,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你會看到我多懂得討長輩的歡心</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

582
00:34:51,800 --> 00:34:53,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我開始痛了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

583
00:34:55,040 --> 00:34:56,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>表示我們快到了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

584
00:34:58,200 --> 00:34:59,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>寶貝，你覺得如何？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

585
00:35:00,240 --> 00:35:02,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你覺得溫納姆的破爛街道怎麼樣？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

586
00:35:02,720 --> 00:35:04,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這是媽媽長大的地方</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

587
00:35:07,480 --> 00:35:08,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>沒錯</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

588
00:35:20,400 --> 00:35:22,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>拍我，幫我拍張照</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

589
00:35:25,520 --> 00:35:27,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒，房子真不錯</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

590
00:35:29,680 --> 00:35:30,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>有點熱</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

591
00:35:34,720 --> 00:35:36,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他們到了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

592
00:35:37,000 --> 00:35:38,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你好啊</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

593
00:35:38,720 --> 00:35:40,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>怎麼樣？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

594
00:35:40,800 --> 00:35:42,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>家族婚禮</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

595
00:35:42,160 --> 00:35:43,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-見鬼了</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-你好</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

596
00:35:45,320 --> 00:35:46,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你好嗎？我是安德魯</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

597
00:35:46,880 --> 00:35:48,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>安德魯，克萊夫羅斯威爾</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

598
00:35:48,240 --> 00:35:50,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒小親親</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

599
00:35:51,440 --> 00:35:53,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>寶貝，快到我身邊來</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

600
00:35:54,040 --> 00:35:54,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>搬的新地方很不錯</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

601
00:35:55,040 --> 00:35:57,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對，都很好，房子很漂亮，老兄</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

602
00:35:58,560 --> 00:35:59,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>謝謝你，克萊夫</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

603
00:35:59,680 --> 00:36:01,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你好，你好啊</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

604
00:36:02,440 --> 00:36:05,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-我們十點要做妝髮</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-好</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

605
00:36:06,720 --> 00:36:08,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>安迪的媽媽簡直是噩夢</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

606
00:36:08,760 --> 00:36:11,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她很迷人，但我需要你的保護</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

607
00:36:11,600 --> 00:36:14,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好，我是來任你差遣的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

608
00:36:15,240 --> 00:36:16,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>怎麼樣？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

609
00:36:18,880 --> 00:36:20,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你覺得如何？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

610
00:36:21,080 --> 00:36:24,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我不能穿白色禮服，但又想要有袖子</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

611
00:36:25,880 --> 00:36:27,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>很不錯</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

612
00:36:27,200 --> 00:36:28,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你喜歡嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

613
00:36:29,240 --> 00:36:30,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對，那個…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

614
00:36:30,800 --> 00:36:34,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們今晚要睡在這裡嗎？我去洗床單</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

615
00:36:35,320 --> 00:36:36,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>為什麼？這裡沒有人睡過</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

616
00:36:36,920 --> 00:36:38,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我對貓毛過敏</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

617
00:36:39,160 --> 00:36:40,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

618
00:36:41,000 --> 00:36:42,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>從哪時開始？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

619
00:36:42,240 --> 00:36:43,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>一直是這樣</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

620
00:36:50,760 --> 00:36:52,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我的天啊</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

621
00:36:53,920 --> 00:36:55,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那是象鼻蟲嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

622
00:36:57,280 --> 00:36:59,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>見鬼了，她要怎麼知道</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>櫃子裡放了什麼？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

623
00:37:08,440 --> 00:37:10,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>沾點醬汁</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

624
00:37:11,400 --> 00:37:14,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>行了，來，給你</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

625
00:37:14,440 --> 00:37:16,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好乖</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

626
00:37:16,840 --> 00:37:18,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你看，他很喜歡</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

627
00:37:19,040 --> 00:37:20,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>太多鹽和糖</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

628
00:37:24,320 --> 00:37:26,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他遺傳到他媽媽的肺活量</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

629
00:37:27,560 --> 00:37:29,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她是天生的演員</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

630
00:37:30,040 --> 00:37:33,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你還記得你憑三寸不爛之舌</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>進入音樂劇團嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

631
00:37:33,760 --> 00:37:35,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她記得每個人的台詞</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

632
00:37:35,920 --> 00:37:37,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>每一首歌，不只是她自己的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

633
00:37:37,960 --> 00:37:40,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒超會講睡前故事</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>她會模仿各種聲音</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

634
00:37:41,240 --> 00:37:43,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-還唱很多歌</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-這很重要</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

635
00:37:43,240 --> 00:37:44,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>攸關大腦發育</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

636
00:37:46,160 --> 00:37:48,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們怎麼會碰到這麼體貼的男人？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

637
00:37:49,160 --> 00:37:50,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>運氣</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

638
00:37:50,920 --> 00:37:52,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不是自己的親骨肉，他卻幫忙帶</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

639
00:37:55,600 --> 00:37:57,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>在我們家不做這種區別</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

640
00:37:58,320 --> 00:37:59,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>稱讚你，克萊夫</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

641
00:37:59,720 --> 00:38:02,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你們也該盡快自己生一個吧</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

642
00:38:03,600 --> 00:38:07,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>如果當初我有幫手</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我會工作更久，克萊夫</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

643
00:38:07,080 --> 00:38:09,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-我以前在旅遊業</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-只做了兩年</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

644
00:38:09,880 --> 00:38:12,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-旅遊業？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-不止，超過兩年</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

645
00:38:12,920 --> 00:38:14,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>在那之前</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

646
00:38:14,800 --> 00:38:17,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我打了很長一段時間的網球</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

647
00:38:17,560 --> 00:38:19,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>媽媽曾經為奧運受訓</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

648
00:38:20,240 --> 00:38:21,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>奧運？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

649
00:38:21,280 --> 00:38:25,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>後來，我猜安娜貝兒跟你說過</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我罹患多發性硬化症</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

650
00:38:25,560 --> 00:38:27,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她提過，我很遺憾</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

651
00:38:27,360 --> 00:38:30,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>娜塔莉是我見過最勇敢的女人</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

652
00:38:31,040 --> 00:38:33,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她從不把自己的痛苦加諸在別人身上</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

653
00:38:35,560 --> 00:38:37,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這傢伙是何方神聖？見鬼了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

654
00:38:39,600 --> 00:38:40,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>倒滿？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

655
00:38:41,160 --> 00:38:43,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-不用了，謝謝</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-不要了嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

656
00:38:43,240 --> 00:38:44,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我馬上回來</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

657
00:38:49,840 --> 00:38:51,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>寶貝，你的生意怎麼樣？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

658
00:38:52,440 --> 00:38:53,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你是指我的健康狀況嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

659
00:38:53,800 --> 00:38:55,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不是</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

660
00:38:56,480 --> 00:38:57,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你不在意我的健康？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

661
00:39:00,840 --> 00:39:02,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是腦癌，但沒關係</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

662
00:39:02,800 --> 00:39:05,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你為什麼要在派對上談這個？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

663
00:39:05,480 --> 00:39:07,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這不是派對</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我們剛剛才談到你的多發性硬化症</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

664
00:39:07,880 --> 00:39:10,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但我想跟你聊聊你的生意</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

665
00:39:10,960 --> 00:39:13,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-叫什麼來著？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-有機寶貝</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

666
00:39:13,120 --> 00:39:15,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-是原創的</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-由貝兒親自設計</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

667
00:39:15,200 --> 00:39:18,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>晚飯後我開網站給你看</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>勝過多數專業設計師的作品</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

668
00:39:18,680 --> 00:39:21,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-網站？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-營運得很順利，媽，多謝關心</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

669
00:39:22,480 --> 00:39:23,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>賺很多錢嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

670
00:39:23,960 --> 00:39:24,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>夠用了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

671
00:39:26,320 --> 00:39:29,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她給自己很大的壓力，克萊夫</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

672
00:39:29,520 --> 00:39:32,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你要多加留意，現在這是你的工作了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

673
00:39:34,000 --> 00:39:38,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你還記得你高中時志向多遠大嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

674
00:39:39,440 --> 00:39:41,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我高中時沒住在這裡</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

675
00:39:43,360 --> 00:39:44,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我12歲就逃家了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

676
00:39:46,080 --> 00:39:47,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你沒注意到</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

677
00:39:48,320 --> 00:39:50,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好吧，即使在小學</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

678
00:39:50,600 --> 00:39:52,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她喜歡看各種節目</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

679
00:39:52,240 --> 00:39:53,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>個性很活潑</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

680
00:39:54,560 --> 00:39:58,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>《海外特派員》</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>《時事搶先看》、《60分鐘》</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

681
00:39:58,920 --> 00:40:01,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-她會…</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-克萊夫不需要知道這些事</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

682
00:40:01,080 --> 00:40:02,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>…練習採訪</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

683
00:40:02,760 --> 00:40:04,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>騷擾街上每個鄰居</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

684
00:40:06,520 --> 00:40:08,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>可愛至極的小東西</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

685
00:40:08,480 --> 00:40:13,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>挺著小胖肚走在街上</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>手裡拿著假麥克風</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

686
00:40:13,760 --> 00:40:17,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她昭告全世界：“我以後會上電視”</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

687
00:40:21,040 --> 00:40:22,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>現在看看你</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

688
00:40:22,920 --> 00:40:24,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>都長這麼大了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

689
00:40:25,480 --> 00:40:26,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>成為人妻</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

690
00:40:28,400 --> 00:40:30,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>某人的妻子</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

691
00:40:30,240 --> 00:40:31,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們沒結婚</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

692
00:40:32,560 --> 00:40:34,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>伴侶，不好意思</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

693
00:40:35,720 --> 00:40:37,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>還是一個母親，別忘了這點</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

694
00:40:38,000 --> 00:40:39,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>而且開心</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

695
00:40:39,800 --> 00:40:42,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我沒見過你這麼開心</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

696
00:40:43,560 --> 00:40:46,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你以前覺得自己應該達成很多目標</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

697
00:40:47,680 --> 00:40:50,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>最後都順利實現了，很妙吧？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

698
00:40:56,920 --> 00:40:59,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我想那個小男孩還沒吃飽</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

699
00:40:59,680 --> 00:41:01,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-還要香腸嗎？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-給他一個</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

700
00:41:04,680 --> 00:41:05,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>魚雷來了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

701
00:41:06,880 --> 00:41:07,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>看，他很喜歡</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

702
00:41:18,880 --> 00:41:19,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>剛剛真的是…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

703
00:41:23,960 --> 00:41:26,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你12歲就逃家了？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

704
00:41:27,720 --> 00:41:28,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

705
00:41:29,200 --> 00:41:30,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你去了哪裡？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

706
00:41:30,840 --> 00:41:33,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你知道我幾歲才知道床單要換嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

707
00:41:34,960 --> 00:41:36,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我本來不知道床單必須更換</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

708
00:41:38,800 --> 00:41:43,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她讓我睡在髒床單上…好幾年</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

709
00:41:43,600 --> 00:41:44,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我知道了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

710
00:41:45,760 --> 00:41:46,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>可惡</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

711
00:41:51,560 --> 00:41:53,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我不是泛泛之輩</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

712
00:41:57,520 --> 00:41:58,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>為了熬過她的摧殘</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

713
00:41:59,760 --> 00:42:00,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我變得卓越不凡</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

714
00:42:03,280 --> 00:42:04,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我沒有選擇</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

715
00:42:14,560 --> 00:42:16,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（改變你的生活）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

716
00:42:21,040 --> 00:42:24,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（用食物療癒自己</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>無糖、無乳製品、無不良添加物）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

717
00:42:39,960 --> 00:42:41,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（今天是簽書會！）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

718
00:42:46,080 --> 00:42:47,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（徹底的自愛與療癒）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

719
00:42:48,320 --> 00:42:50,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（今天就自我療癒！）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

720
00:43:05,960 --> 00:43:07,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（小蜜，我在布里斯本！）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

721
00:43:07,840 --> 00:43:10,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（要去見你了！）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

722
00:43:26,360 --> 00:43:27,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（挑一個禮物袋）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

723
00:43:27,440 --> 00:43:28,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（《從地獄到療癒》）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

724
00:43:44,040 --> 00:43:46,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-感覺如何？不會太累吧？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-不會，感覺很好</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

725
00:43:49,320 --> 00:43:50,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>很漂亮</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

726
00:43:58,800 --> 00:44:02,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>大家好</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>天啊，你們看起來都明亮動人</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

727
00:44:02,160 --> 00:44:04,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>多好看的一群人</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

728
00:44:05,080 --> 00:44:06,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你們可能已經認識我了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

729
00:44:06,680 --> 00:44:09,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但我在想我們可以先做點活動</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

730
00:44:09,160 --> 00:44:11,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>互相認識一下</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

731
00:44:11,880 --> 00:44:14,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>所以請轉向你身邊的人</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

732
00:44:14,640 --> 00:44:16,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>打個招呼，自我介紹</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

733
00:44:16,720 --> 00:44:19,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>可以擊掌、擁抱，就是這樣</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

734
00:44:19,840 --> 00:44:22,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>因為我們聚在這裡的原因</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>是出於痛苦，對吧？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

735
00:44:22,720 --> 00:44:25,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>或是感到疲憊、難過</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

736
00:44:25,280 --> 00:44:27,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們想要擺脫那種感覺</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

737
00:44:27,400 --> 00:44:31,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我要你們讓肺裡充滿愛</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

738
00:44:31,880 --> 00:44:32,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>與感恩</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

739
00:44:34,640 --> 00:44:36,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>現在吐氣</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

740
00:44:37,960 --> 00:44:39,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>然後這個帥哥…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

741
00:44:41,400 --> 00:44:42,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>當時他還不是我的男人</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

742
00:44:44,960 --> 00:44:46,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>給了我一塊石頭</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

743
00:44:48,440 --> 00:44:51,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>它提醒我</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>這個世界遠比我們所想的更神奇</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

744
00:44:53,040 --> 00:44:55,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們只是不相信</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

745
00:44:57,000 --> 00:44:58,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>就在那一刻</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

746
00:44:59,240 --> 00:45:01,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我開始不用頭腦思考</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

747
00:45:02,240 --> 00:45:05,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>而是用我的身體去感受</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

748
00:45:08,240 --> 00:45:10,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好，聽夠悲傷的故事了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

749
00:45:10,240 --> 00:45:12,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>大家站起來，快點</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

750
00:45:13,480 --> 00:45:14,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>讓我們一起甩掉</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

751
00:45:17,080 --> 00:45:19,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>釋放所有的負能量</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

752
00:45:19,240 --> 00:45:21,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>以及任何阻礙你的東西</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

753
00:45:21,080 --> 00:45:22,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你現在變回白紙了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

754
00:45:22,960 --> 00:45:25,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你們的袋子裡有一個氣球</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>把它拿在手中</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

755
00:45:25,640 --> 00:45:27,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我要你們腦中想一個念頭</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

756
00:45:27,680 --> 00:45:30,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>然後把它吹進氣球裡，開始</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

757
00:45:55,800 --> 00:45:58,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我在浴室裡踩到毛巾滑倒了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

758
00:45:58,280 --> 00:46:01,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>骨盆有兩處骨折</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

759
00:46:01,320 --> 00:46:03,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不到兩個月前的事</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

760
00:46:03,840 --> 00:46:05,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我這把年紀有兩處骨折？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

761
00:46:06,440 --> 00:46:10,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你得接受以後再也下不了床的事實</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

762
00:46:23,320 --> 00:46:26,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我父親也發生過類似的慘案</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>書上有X光片</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

763
00:46:27,440 --> 00:46:28,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你們都拿到書了嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

764
00:46:32,040 --> 00:46:34,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你沒有點頭</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

765
00:46:34,760 --> 00:46:36,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好漂亮的臉蛋</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

766
00:46:36,640 --> 00:46:37,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>像一顆愛心</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

767
00:46:39,040 --> 00:46:40,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你拿到書了嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

768
00:46:42,800 --> 00:46:44,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我訂了，但沒有及時送達</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

769
00:46:44,880 --> 00:46:47,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>如果沒有書，來這裡毫無意義</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

770
00:46:48,480 --> 00:46:51,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你今天會買這本書吧，麻煩你？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

771
00:46:51,240 --> 00:46:52,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>會</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

772
00:46:53,320 --> 00:46:55,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-抱歉</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-那就開始吧</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

773
00:46:55,480 --> 00:46:56,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你說你看過書</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

774
00:46:56,840 --> 00:46:58,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-50年前…</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-我讀過文章</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

775
00:46:58,800 --> 00:47:02,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>…我父親華特想到你們</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

776
00:47:02,600 --> 00:47:04,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（華特赫希醫生</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>《重振絕望》）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

777
00:47:06,600 --> 00:47:07,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你說得對</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

778
00:47:08,720 --> 00:47:10,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們應該先讀完書的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

779
00:47:11,160 --> 00:47:12,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>也許你們當時還沒準備好</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

780
00:47:13,480 --> 00:47:19,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我對你建議八到十二個月</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>不做掃描的想法很好奇</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

781
00:47:19,800 --> 00:47:21,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對，至少要這麼久</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

782
00:47:21,600 --> 00:47:24,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>腫瘤科醫生克制不了</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>動不動就要掃描、掃描、掃描</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

783
00:47:24,680 --> 00:47:26,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他們喜歡那些巨大機器</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

784
00:47:26,880 --> 00:47:30,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>每照一次我們都變得更虛弱</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

785
00:47:30,840 --> 00:47:35,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你知道有多少毒素</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>都是經由這些機器傳送的嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

786
00:47:35,480 --> 00:47:39,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但你要怎麼追蹤癌症是否有擴散？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

787
00:47:39,840 --> 00:47:41,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你怎麼知道我不是騙子？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

788
00:47:42,280 --> 00:47:43,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我父親不是騙子</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

789
00:47:43,960 --> 00:47:46,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不，我只是說如果沒有資料的話…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

790
00:47:46,560 --> 00:47:47,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你是媽媽</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

791
00:47:47,800 --> 00:47:49,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>擔心是你的職責</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

792
00:47:49,720 --> 00:47:50,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她是個特別的女孩</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

793
00:47:51,040 --> 00:47:52,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是啊</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

794
00:47:52,720 --> 00:47:54,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我最近在看她的部落格</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

795
00:47:54,800 --> 00:47:55,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>文筆很好</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

796
00:47:56,880 --> 00:47:58,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>需要加入更多影片內容</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

797
00:47:59,000 --> 00:48:01,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>也許她喜歡這裡，可以介紹一下我們</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

798
00:48:01,840 --> 00:48:04,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>成為品牌大使</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

799
00:48:04,960 --> 00:48:07,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>看她的意願</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我們的生意多到應接不暇了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

800
00:48:12,320 --> 00:48:13,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你為什麼來這裡？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

801
00:48:14,400 --> 00:48:15,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你知道原因了嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

802
00:48:22,840 --> 00:48:24,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我媽得了腸癌</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

803
00:48:30,920 --> 00:48:32,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她討厭化療</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

804
00:48:32,960 --> 00:48:35,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>當然，那是毒藥</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

805
00:48:36,800 --> 00:48:38,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>而且無效</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

806
00:48:40,840 --> 00:48:42,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她生前搬來跟我們住</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

807
00:48:44,560 --> 00:48:45,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我照顧她</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

808
00:48:46,480 --> 00:48:49,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>把她抱上馬桶，再抱她下來</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

809
00:48:49,440 --> 00:48:50,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是啊</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

810
00:48:50,920 --> 00:48:54,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她走不動，吃不下東西，不能自理</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

811
00:48:54,400 --> 00:48:55,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>糟透了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

812
00:48:56,400 --> 00:48:58,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你們兩個都很痛苦</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

813
00:49:00,280 --> 00:49:02,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>所以你知道那種治療行不通</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

814
00:49:07,080 --> 00:49:08,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你是為了希望而來</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

815
00:49:10,560 --> 00:49:11,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這個理由很充分</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

816
00:49:16,040 --> 00:49:18,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>華特，我父親</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

817
00:49:19,200 --> 00:49:20,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是德國人，有猶太血統</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

818
00:49:21,800 --> 00:49:24,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他在第一次世界大戰後三餐不繼</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

819
00:49:24,520 --> 00:49:26,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我看書上說他有…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

820
00:49:26,200 --> 00:49:28,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>偏頭痛，對，從小就讓他飽受折磨</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

821
00:49:29,040 --> 00:49:31,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>然而，就在他挨餓的階段</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

822
00:49:32,000 --> 00:49:33,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他的身體開始痊癒</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

823
00:49:33,800 --> 00:49:35,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（《從地獄到療癒》）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

824
00:49:38,360 --> 00:49:41,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我想跟你聊聊關於我的姊妹的事</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

825
00:49:41,720 --> 00:49:43,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她現在很不好過</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

826
00:49:43,240 --> 00:49:45,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她在找替代療法，看過很多醫生…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

827
00:49:45,920 --> 00:49:50,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>因為醫院剛告知她噩耗</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

828
00:49:50,200 --> 00:49:51,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她真的有點…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

829
00:49:52,040 --> 00:49:53,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>嗨，親愛的，你會沒空吃的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

830
00:49:53,720 --> 00:49:55,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不，沒關係，我要喝果汁</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

831
00:49:56,440 --> 00:49:59,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>如果她考慮接受赫希療法</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我很樂意替她講解</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

832
00:49:59,800 --> 00:50:03,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-你要留下她的聯絡資料嗎？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-你需要經紀人幫你處理這些諮詢</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

833
00:50:03,280 --> 00:50:05,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我有一個經紀人</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

834
00:50:05,520 --> 00:50:08,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>太棒了，我都不知道</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

835
00:50:08,720 --> 00:50:10,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她在做放射治療</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

836
00:50:10,400 --> 00:50:13,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但醫生說已經轉移到淋巴結了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

837
00:50:13,720 --> 00:50:14,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我很喜歡這次的活動</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

838
00:50:15,000 --> 00:50:16,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>全身起雞皮疙瘩</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

839
00:50:16,640 --> 00:50:17,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>謝謝你來參加</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

840
00:50:20,480 --> 00:50:21,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

841
00:50:21,440 --> 00:50:22,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

842
00:50:22,480 --> 00:50:24,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我是蜜拉，這位是…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

843
00:50:24,120 --> 00:50:26,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-莫琳</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-莫琳，抱歉</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

844
00:50:26,160 --> 00:50:27,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不，我是…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

845
00:50:28,200 --> 00:50:29,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我是貝兒</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

846
00:50:30,520 --> 00:50:31,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒吉柏森</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

847
00:50:32,800 --> 00:50:33,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

848
00:50:34,760 --> 00:50:35,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>自身免疫疾病</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

849
00:50:38,120 --> 00:50:40,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-腦癌</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-對</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

850
00:50:42,120 --> 00:50:46,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-你好嗎？你看起來氣色很好</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-我們可以出去散個步，好好聊嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

851
00:50:46,080 --> 00:50:48,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>街角有一間咖啡廳，我下載了菜單</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

852
00:50:48,680 --> 00:50:51,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-看起來很安全</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-我媽在這裡，所以…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

853
00:50:51,160 --> 00:50:54,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>塔瑪拉來了，我也想跟她打聲招呼</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

854
00:50:55,640 --> 00:50:58,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們得回家了，抱歉，我得喝果汁</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

855
00:50:58,880 --> 00:51:01,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我有個點子想跟你討論</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

856
00:51:01,160 --> 00:51:04,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>可以追蹤進度</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>有自動功能，就像飲食計畫一樣</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

857
00:51:04,760 --> 00:51:07,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>真的很抱歉，我只是…我真的得走了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

858
00:51:07,200 --> 00:51:09,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>請你的姊妹隨時聯絡我</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

859
00:51:09,600 --> 00:51:11,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-好，非常感謝</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-再見</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

860
00:51:17,160 --> 00:51:19,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你研究過用葉酸提升免疫力嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

861
00:51:20,960 --> 00:51:24,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>乾燥豆類、豌豆</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>小扁豆、肝臟、蘆筍？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

862
00:51:56,720 --> 00:51:58,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她自己母親的婚禮</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

863
00:51:59,000 --> 00:51:59,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是啊</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

864
00:52:00,040 --> 00:52:01,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我只拜託過她這麼一件事</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

865
00:52:01,880 --> 00:52:04,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>都是因為頭痛的關係</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

866
00:52:04,320 --> 00:52:08,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>一旦發作</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>她就得進入黑暗的房間減壓</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

867
00:52:08,520 --> 00:52:09,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但我會勸勸她</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

868
00:52:10,360 --> 00:52:11,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我會的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

869
00:52:11,400 --> 00:52:13,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她不會聽你的話</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

870
00:52:16,080 --> 00:52:20,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>其實呢，關於安娜貝兒的演技</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我沒有誇大</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

871
00:52:21,480 --> 00:52:25,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我永遠忘不了她被第一個男友甩了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

872
00:52:26,280 --> 00:52:28,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她假裝心臟病發</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

873
00:52:28,680 --> 00:52:31,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>演得超逼真，他們還叫了救護車</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

874
00:52:33,400 --> 00:52:34,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>很耳熟吧？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

875
00:52:42,280 --> 00:52:43,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你的車到了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

876
00:53:12,520 --> 00:53:13,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>媽媽說了什麼？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

877
00:53:17,240 --> 00:53:18,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>沒有</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

878
00:53:20,720 --> 00:53:22,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>一定有</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

879
00:53:25,960 --> 00:53:26,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>怎樣？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

880
00:53:27,560 --> 00:53:29,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是關於我的健康嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

881
00:53:29,840 --> 00:53:31,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她不喜歡…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

882
00:53:32,080 --> 00:53:35,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她不喜歡被別人分走關注</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

883
00:53:38,720 --> 00:53:39,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>六點來接你</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

884
00:53:40,000 --> 00:53:41,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>今天我要拆人工血管</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

885
00:53:42,040 --> 00:53:44,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>會耗很久，我們回家見，愛你</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

886
00:53:45,000 --> 00:53:46,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>給你一個大親親</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

887
00:53:46,360 --> 00:53:47,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-再見</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-再見</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

888
00:53:47,320 --> 00:53:48,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>再見，寶貝</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

889
00:53:49,520 --> 00:53:52,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（癌症閃邊去）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

890
00:54:07,880 --> 00:54:09,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>媽咪忘記拿筆電了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

891
00:54:10,400 --> 00:54:11,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>真是笨媽咪</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

892
00:54:12,760 --> 00:54:15,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不，我們這裡不做化療</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

893
00:54:15,560 --> 00:54:17,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我剛剛送我的伴侶到大門口</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

894
00:54:18,000 --> 00:54:20,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你確定今天是做化療嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

895
00:54:20,160 --> 00:54:21,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們有一間乳房診所</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

896
00:54:21,480 --> 00:54:22,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是化療</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

897
00:54:22,400 --> 00:54:23,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她今天要拆人工血管</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

898
00:54:24,600 --> 00:54:25,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好吧</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

899
00:54:26,720 --> 00:54:28,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-可以請問一下嗎？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-好</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

900
00:54:28,440 --> 00:54:30,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是哪一種癌症？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

901
00:54:39,840 --> 00:54:40,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>嗯</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

902
00:54:42,520 --> 00:54:43,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那個…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

903
00:54:44,400 --> 00:54:46,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>沒事了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

904
00:55:12,280 --> 00:55:14,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們再也不必回去那裡</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

905
00:55:39,280 --> 00:55:42,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我是說，不是現在，但…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

906
00:55:44,320 --> 00:55:48,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我想試試生個孩子</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

907
00:55:50,520 --> 00:55:51,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>如果你願意的話</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

908
00:55:56,880 --> 00:55:57,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

909
00:56:01,800 --> 00:56:03,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我一定要停止治療</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

910
00:56:03,560 --> 00:56:06,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>反正腦霧很嚴重，什麼事都做不了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

911
00:56:06,720 --> 00:56:10,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我想我早就知道了</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我不再聽從自己的直覺</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

912
00:56:12,560 --> 00:56:14,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我要關閉有機寶貝</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

913
00:56:15,960 --> 00:56:17,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>概念太狹隘了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

914
00:56:18,040 --> 00:56:20,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那只算是新創企業</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

915
00:56:20,840 --> 00:56:24,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>第一個總是以失敗收場</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>成功的永遠是第二個</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

916
00:56:25,360 --> 00:56:28,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>部落格已死，發聲網絡太小</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

917
00:56:29,640 --> 00:56:31,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我不需要接受別人喝采</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

918
00:56:32,720 --> 00:56:34,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我想打造一個應用程式</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

919
00:56:35,920 --> 00:56:38,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>可以追蹤食譜與提供健康建議</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

920
00:56:39,960 --> 00:56:41,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>就像是食物日記</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

921
00:56:43,040 --> 00:56:45,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>所以你能隨時掌握儲藏室裡有什麼</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

922
00:56:47,200 --> 00:56:49,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>隨時知道你把什麼東西吃下肚</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

923
00:56:50,520 --> 00:56:52,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>想要好好的就要保持健康</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

924
00:56:54,000 --> 00:56:56,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我想要在每個人的手機裡</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

925
00:56:57,240 --> 00:56:58,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（@療癒貝兒）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

926
00:56:58,440 --> 00:57:00,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>融入每一餐</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

927
00:57:00,520 --> 00:57:02,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（65.7萬粉絲</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>230萬粉絲）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

928
00:57:02,400 --> 00:57:05,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>只要一手就能掌握</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

929
00:57:05,680 --> 00:57:06,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>就像教練</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

930
00:57:07,840 --> 00:57:10,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>或是媽媽，提醒你要照顧好自己</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

931
00:57:11,640 --> 00:57:13,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>也像是朋友</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

932
00:57:14,480 --> 00:57:16,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>它就像你最好的朋友</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

933
00:57:16,680 --> 00:57:18,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（甜菜根果泥</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>蘑菇漢堡）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

934
00:57:23,040 --> 00:57:24,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-嗨</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-嗨</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

935
00:57:27,240 --> 00:57:28,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>工作怎麼樣？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

936
00:57:28,720 --> 00:57:30,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>很有趣</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

937
00:57:30,360 --> 00:57:32,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不如我們去吃飲茶吧？我慢慢告訴你</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

938
00:57:33,680 --> 00:57:35,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>也許不要吃飲茶</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

939
00:57:36,720 --> 00:57:39,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對，餃子不在飲食計畫中</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

940
00:57:40,600 --> 00:57:41,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>應用程式上沒有</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

941
00:57:41,920 --> 00:57:42,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你還好嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

942
00:57:43,600 --> 00:57:44,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你好像很焦躁</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

943
00:57:45,720 --> 00:57:47,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她是假的，小露</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

944
00:57:48,280 --> 00:57:49,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我有個爆料者認識她</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

945
00:57:49,520 --> 00:57:52,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她一個親近的朋友從街上跑進來說</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

946
00:57:52,400 --> 00:57:56,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒吉柏森捏造她的所有癌症診斷</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

947
00:57:58,560 --> 00:58:00,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不，她沒有</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

948
00:58:02,160 --> 00:58:03,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我要你刪除應用程式</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

949
00:58:03,680 --> 00:58:04,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我見過她本人</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

950
00:58:06,000 --> 00:58:06,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她病了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

951
00:58:06,920 --> 00:58:08,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我不這麼認為</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

952
00:58:08,960 --> 00:58:11,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她的行為很卑鄙險惡</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

953
00:58:12,240 --> 00:58:14,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-你認真想想看</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-她在做好事</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

954
00:58:15,480 --> 00:58:17,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>真正幫助他人的好事</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

955
00:58:17,840 --> 00:58:18,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>媽的，她在利用你</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

956
00:58:19,800 --> 00:58:22,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-你為什麼這麼蠢？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-你幹嘛對我大吼？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

957
00:58:29,520 --> 00:58:30,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>抱歉</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

958
00:58:31,200 --> 00:58:34,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>賈斯汀，你知道露西不在場</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我不能跟你談</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

959
00:58:34,160 --> 00:58:36,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我知道，是《時代報》的一篇報導</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

960
00:58:36,960 --> 00:58:39,360
